Package logic.generators.facades

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OrderFacade
    The logic-facade for any order-DAO operation, the data Layer and Presentation layer both goes through this layer when sending/recieving information, consider each layer closed This interface uses multiple DAO's for mysql, but an implementation could decide to only use one if desired
    UserFacade
    The logic facade for any DAO-user operation, the data Layer and Presentation layer both goes through this layer when sending/recieving information, consider each layer closed This interface uses one DAO for MYSQL, but multiple can be implemented if desired
